Achievements.Name: My Availability
Achievements.Description: Set up your "My Availability" settings online.

Achievements.Name: 1 Online Ranked Win
Achievements.Description: Win one online ranked match.

Achievements.Name: 10 Online Ranked Win
Achievements.Description: Win ten online ranked matches.

Achievements.Name: 20 Online Ranked Wins
Achievements.Description: Win twenty online ranked matches.

Achievements.Name: Streak of 3 Ranked Wins
Achievements.Description: Get three consecutive wins in Online Ranked Matches.  Must play at least two unique opponents.

Achievements.Name: Streak of 5 Ranked Wins
Achievements.Description: Get five consecutive wins in Online Ranked Matches.  Must play at least three unique opponents.

Achievements.Name: Streak of 7 Ranked Wins
Achievements.Description: Get seven consecutive wins in Online Ranked Matches.  Must play at least three unique opponents.

Achievements.Name: Congenial Award
Achievements.Description: Achieve an 80% or better feedback rating with at least 10 feedbacks.

Achievements.Name: Super Congenial Award
Achievements.Description: Achieve an 85% or better feedback rating with at least 20 feedbacks.

Achievements.Name: Online Guru
Achievements.Description: Accumulate 10+ online hours of playing time from online gameplay.

Achievements.Name: Hard-earned Win
Achievements.Description: Finish and win an Online Ranked Match w/ a school rated 65 or lower, against a school rated 80+.

Achievements.Name: Big Game Hunt
Achievements.Description: Beat an opponent that is currently ranked in the Top 300 on the Overall Leaderboard (complete game).

Achievements.Name: Bigger Game Hunt
Achievements.Description: Beat an opponent that is currently ranked in the Top 100 on the Overall Leaderboard (complete game).

Achievements.Name: Cruel "D"
Achievements.Description: Hold an opponent to 40 points or less in an Online Ranked Match (complete game).

Achievements.Name: Merciless "D"
Achievements.Description: Hold an opponent to 25 points or less in an Online Ranked Match (complete game).

Achievements.Name: Online Tourney Win
Achievements.Description: Win an Online Tournament game.

Achievements.Name: Online Tourney Champ
Achievements.Description: Be crowned the overall Champion in an Online Tournament.

Achievements.Name: Online League Win
Achievements.Description: Win an Online League game.

Achievements.Name: Pontiac (Online)
Achievements.Description: Qualify for the Pontiac VirtualÂ® Final 4Â® and complete at least one game in the tournament.

Achievements.Name: Dish It Out
Achievements.Description: Get 25 or more assists in a game with any team.

Achievements.Name: Rejections
Achievements.Description: Get 15 or more blocks in a game with any team.

Achievements.Name: Sneaky
Achievements.Description: Get 15 or more steals in a game with any team.

Achievements.Name: Long Distance
Achievements.Description: Make at least 15 3PT field goals in a game with any team.

Achievements.Name: Bench Help
Achievements.Description: Score 40 or more points in a game with your bench players.

Achievements.Name: Dish It Out Carefully
Achievements.Description: Get 25 or more assists in a game and commit 10 or fewer turnovers.

Achievements.Name: Accuracy
Achievements.Description: Attempt at least 35 FG and make at least 65% of your shots.

Achievements.Name: Long Range Accuracy
Achievements.Description: Attempt at least 15 3PT shots, and make at least 60% of your shots.

Achievements.Name: Inside Game
Achievements.Description: Score 50 or more points in the paint with any team.

Achievements.Name: Clutch Factor
Achievements.Description: Win a game with a buzzer beater shot.

Achievements.Name: Duke vs. North Carolina Rivalry
Achievements.Description: Win this rivalry as either Duke or North Carolina in MOP difficulty setting.

Achievements.Name: Kentucky vs. Louisville Rivalry
Achievements.Description: Win this rivalry as either Kentucky or Louisville in MOP difficulty setting.

Achievements.Name: Arizona vs. UCLA Rivalry
Achievements.Description: Win this rivalry as either Arizona or UCLA in MOP difficulty setting.

Achievements.Name: David and Goliath
Achievements.Description: Beat the CPU school rated 80+ using a school rated 65 or lower.  MOP difficulty, 10 minute half.

Achievements.Name: Free Throws Are Easy
Achievements.Description: Shoot 90% or better in Free Throw Practice Mode. Minimum of 100 shots.

Achievements.Name: Coaching Talent
Achievements.Description: Beat CPU in Coach Mode. All-Conf difficulty and 10 minute half. Both teams within 5 rating points.

Achievements.Name: Coaching Master
Achievements.Description: Beat CPU in Coach Mode. All-Am difficulty and 10 minute half. Both teams within 5 rating points.

Achievements.Name: Coaching Guru
Achievements.Description: Beat CPU in Coach Mode. MOP difficulty and 10 minute half. Both teams within 5 rating points.

Achievements.Name: Campus Collector
Achievements.Description: Buy every item in the Campus Store.

Achievements.Name: Individual Record Breaker (Glitched Achievement)
Achievements.Description: Break all NCAA individual single-game records.

Achievements.Name: Team Record Breaker (Glitched Achievement)
Achievements.Description: Break all NCAA school single-game records.

Achievements.Name: Beat 'em All
Achievements.Description: Beat all schools in the game.  Any game mode or settings.

Achievements.Name: Career Winner
Achievements.Description: Get through 5 years in Career Legacy mode, and achieve a win percentage of 75% or higher.

Achievements.Name: Conquered Legacy
Achievements.Description: Complete all Legacy Goals in Legacy Career Mode.

Achievements.Name: Ranked in the Polls
Achievements.Description: In Legacy Career mode, earn a spot in the Top 25 polls in your first year.

Achievements.Name: Legacy Champion
Achievements.Description: Win a National Championship in Legacy Mode (Career only)

Achievements.Name: Legacy Champion 2x
Achievements.Description: Win 2 National Championships in Legacy Mode (Career only)

Achievements.Name: Legacy Champion 3x
Achievements.Description: Win 3 National Championships in Legacy Mode (Career only)

Achievements.Name: Pontiac Tournament (Offline)
Achievements.Description: Complete and win a Pontiac NCAAÂ® Tournament. Must play all games as the same school w/o simulating.

Achievements.Name: Online League Champ
Achievements.Description: Be crowned the overall Champion in an Online League.
